  "prompt": "How much money does Supercell make in a day?",
  "response": "Supercell, the Finnish mobile game developer, is known for popular games like Clash of Clans, Clash Royale, and Brawl Stars. While the company does not publicly disclose its daily revenue, we can make an educated estimate based on available data.\n\nIn 2022, Supercell reported annual revenues of approximately $1.8 billion. To calculate their daily revenue, we can divide this annual figure by the number of days in a year:\n\n$1,800,000,000 \u00f7 365 \u2248 $4,931,507 per day\n\nPlease note that this is a rough estimate and actual daily revenues may vary due to factors like seasonal fluctuations, new game releases, and in-game events. Nonetheless, this calculation gives you a general idea of Supercell's daily earnings.",
